      <title>Math Test</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/test-math/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 15 Dec 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/test-math/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Here are some test equations:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Inline: $\alpha + \beta = \gamma$&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Display:
$$
\begin{aligned}
\dot{x} &amp;amp; = \sigma(y-x) \
\dot{y} &amp;amp; = \rho x - y - xz \
\dot{z} &amp;amp; = -\beta z + xy
\end{aligned}
$$&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
